data.description: Strong beautiful Colonial home with a wrap-around porch. Original hardwood floors, new 2" faux wood blinds, 9 new ceiling fans, all new interior doors with french doors in the dining room and kitchen, new interior paint. Kitchen cabinets have all new doors and drawers, new dishwasher, stove & garbage disposal-the refrigerator is older but included if desired. Plush new carpeting in the master bedroom. This home has a lot of updates including electric, plumbing, and roof in 2014. She's a unique beauty and being sold as-is!
data.whatILove: I love to imagine what these walls have seen over the past 120 years. The home is strong and feels safe with so much room to roam about. The up and coming neighborhood is quiet and peaceful with kind and friendly neighbors and both historic houses across the street are now being renovated. We love sitting on the large porch to watch it rain, gaze at the stars in the evening, or just feel blessed.
